    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a reliable ride that's been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure, you've found it! This beauty runs like a charm and has served me so well. It\u2019s got a few tiny signs of character from the road, but overall it\u2019s in really solid shape and super clean inside. I\u2019m honestly sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019ll make the next owner very happy. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
